entries.journal_entry_description: You are to find the missing soldier on the Station Gamma.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Either use the Gamma Shuttle system, or fly your own space craft.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Travel to Station Gamma Via the Shuttle or Your Ship
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You are to search the Station Gamma for the missing soldier. If you find him, dead or alive, you are to bring back proof of what happened to him.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Return to the Tansarii space station, your mission here is complete.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Ysanna with the datapad
